list.abstract: member（英 [ˈmembə]，美 [ˈmembər]），英语单词，作名词为成员；会员；构件。短语搭配有family member（家庭成员）。例句为“Now I am a League member.（现在我是一名团员。）” member相关近义词有fellow、insider，相关反义词有nonmember。
「Member」是动漫作品《魔法禁书目录》中学园都市统括理事长亚雷斯塔·克劳利直属暗部组织「Member」。10月9日的事件中主要的任务消灭叛变的暗部组织「School」和「Block」，但在第二十三学区其成员死角移动的查乐被一方通行杀死，而首领博士也在第四学区袭击「School」的垣根帝督时被秒杀，组织旋即解体。

yingyinNormal.en: President, only member, and harshest critic.
yingyinNormal.zh: 主席，唯一成员，最严厉的批评家。

yingyinNormal.en: I'd hate to be responsible for the death of a family member. Wouldn't you agree, Simba?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不喜欢为家族成员的死亡来负责，你同意吗？辛巴。

yingyinNormal.en: You think? Of course. How does the cheetah attack a herd of wildebeests? By going after its weakest member.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真的吗？当然，猎豹是怎么对付牛羚群的追杀最弱小的成员。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, at the time, the owner of the Gaffney First Bank was a member of the Klan. Some of you know that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当时，加夫尼第一银行的行长是三K党的成员。这在座的一些人知道。

yingyinNormal.en: Good eye, Kowalski. And once again, you've proved that you are a meaningful and valued member of this team.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好眼力，科沃斯基，你再次证明了自己是我们队伍里有价值的成员。

yingyinNormal.en: I say again, the Nine Eyes committee would have full access to the combined intelligence streams of all member states.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我再说一遍，九眼委员会将有权获得全部成员国的情报信息源。

yingyinNormal.en: The world looked pretty darn good sitting on a haystack in the back of a Ford F 150 as a member of the Corn Queen's court.
yingyinNormal.zh: 作为玉米皇后团的成员之一，坐在福特F150后面放的干草堆上，那是相当的风光啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Those stolen NYPD files contain every member of Elias' organization, his business associates, and the structure of his operation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那些被偷走的纽约警局文件中有全部以利亚组织的成员名单，生意伙伴以及运作架构。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, simple. The Arrah, Arrah in the riddle meant Jan Arrah a member of the Legion of Superheroes, known as Element Lad.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很简单，谜语里的Arrah， Arrah指的是Jan Arrah，超级英雄军团的一名成员，被称为元素少年。

yingyinNormal.en: Actually, as the newest member of your social group, I believe I'll gain more acceptance by arbitrarily siding with your friends from time to time. Shrewd.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其实作为你们这个社交团体的最新成员，我觉得偶尔偏向你们的朋友们一方更能让我融入你们。真阴险。

yingyinNormal.en: When I first came into this family, I didn't think I was ever going to be accepted. Then, one day, Alex needed to write a report about a family member, and she picked me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我刚刚来到这个家时，我以为我永远不会被你们接纳。直到有一天，艾丽克斯要写关于某个家庭成员的报告，她选了我。

yingyinNormal.en: We've a plan. Different codes will be given to each member of command. When the bombers claim credit for the next attack, you'll tell us which word they use.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们有个计划。指挥部里的每位成员都使用不同的暗号，袭击者下一次行动后 会宣称对袭击负责，你告诉我，他们使用了哪个暗号。

yingyinNormal.en: We wanted to make sure our newest member got home safely. Thanks, guys. See you next week. Keep up with the program. Dolly. Remember, fish are friends, not food! Bye!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们想要确保我们的新成员安全到家。谢谢，伙计们，下礼拜见。训练计划一定要进行下去。记住,鱼类是朋友不是食物！再见!

yingyinNormal.en: What do you mean? Leonard's a member.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这话什么意思？莱纳德是会员啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Who's my favorite member of NSYNC? Justin.
yingyinNormal.zh: "超级男孩"中我最喜欢哪一位？贾斯汀。

yingyinNormal.en: The capybara is the largest member of the rodent family.
yingyinNormal.zh: 水豚是啮齿类动物中为数最多的品种。

yingyinNormal.en: As does your Vulcan crew member, isn't that right, Spock?
yingyinNormal.zh: 就像你的维肯星船员一样，对吗，史波克？

yingyinNormal.en: It's beautiful. Yeah, and Albert Einstein was a member there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 环境很美。是啊，而且阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦曾是会员。

yingyinNormal.en: It's close. And Albert Einstein was a member there. And Albert Einstein was a member there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还很近。而且阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦曾是会员。而且阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦曾是会员。

yingyinNormal.en: After a few hours, a member of my own species found me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 几个小时后，我被一个同类发现。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
